            <h4>What is diabetes?</h4>
            <p>There are two main types of diabetes:</p>

            <ul>
                <li><p><b>Type 1 diabetes</b> is when the pancreas doesn’t produce insulin.</p></li>
                <li><p><b>Type 2 diabetes</b> is when the pancreas either doesn’t produce enough insulin or the body doesn’t use it effectively.</p></li>
            </ul>

